<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/257656-would-a-13-year-old-excellent-student-like">Would a 13 year old excellent student like this book?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_257656'><a id="like_count_community_question_257656" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/257656?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F75503.Roma">like</a></span>

